Eclipse Plug-In Documentation


--------------------------------------------
1. Got to "Help, Software Updates, find and Install..." in your Eclipse workspace 
and select "Search for new Features" on the next screen.
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install01.jpg] Install 1

--------------------------------------------
2. Select "Add new remote Site" and add the URL 
http://is207.infoserve.endress.com:8080/WebGuiToolkit/update/ . 
Confirm with OK. Make sure, the "WGT plugin" checkbox is selected and click "Finish".
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install02.jpg] Install 2

--------------------------------------------
3. Select The "WGT eclipse Feature ..." and click "Next".
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install03.jpg] Install 3

--------------------------------------------
4. Accept the licence, if you agree.
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install04.jpg] Install 4

--------------------------------------------
5. Check overview and click "Finish".
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install05.jpg] Install 5

--------------------------------------------
6. Verify and click "Install".
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install06.jpg] Install 6

--------------------------------------------
7. Restart your eclipse and your done.
--------------------------------------------

[../images/screens/plugin/install07.jpg] Install 7